Hiatus is admitted :

(1) When there is a change of speaker, e. g. 616, 665.

(2) WVhen a line is broken by a strong pause, e.g. 345.

(3) When a word is isolated by the sense, e. g. 264 incertum. (4) After the fourth foot of an Iambic or Trochaic Tetrameter..
